  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774121/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765196735\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774121/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765196735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774121/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765196735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Explore the world with puzzles, fancy mechanisms and dangerous enemies!<br><br>Super Jet Juck is a dynamic platformer game full of skirmishes, puzzles and adventures. Join the heroic team - the fearless soldiers Juck and Tom on an exciting and dangerous journey.<br><br>You can play the game either alone or together on one computer!<br><br>So, you are the captain of a special unit of the army sent to the study of an abandoned space station. Your task is to destroy all defensive systems that have gone out of control!",
  "about_the_game": "Explore the world with puzzles, fancy mechanisms and dangerous enemies!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSuper Jet Juck is a dynamic platformer game full of skirmishes, puzzles and adventures. Join the heroic team - the fearless soldiers Juck and Tom on an exciting and dangerous journey.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can play the game either alone or together on one computer!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo, you are the captain of a special unit of the army sent to the study of an abandoned space station. Your task is to destroy all defensive systems that have gone out of control!",
